{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d1dfef795c","title":"致朱德等电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"bdae165358","index":0,"year":1936,"month":7,"day":null,"articleId":"d1dfef795c"}],"tags":[{"id":"a7ea3bd8ce","name":"朱德","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji8","name":"毛泽东全集第8卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji8.pdf"},{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji8":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"77f1b23bc9","type":"paragraph","text":"致朱德等电\"","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"d1dfef795c"},{"id":"d091187232","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年7月）红二、红四方面军北出草地后应迅速攻占眠州。这样，对打马步芳、毛炳文、王均等部十分有利，“战略上大占优势”两广因无革命决心与内部不巩固，发生内变：然全国革命高涨的基本形势没有变化，从东北来说，统一战线方面又“有了进步”U这是毛译东和周恩来、彭德怀致先德、张国森、任时电的主要内1936年，毛泽东在保安旧居","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"d1dfef795c"}],"page":{"id":"3d663de768","publicationId":"maoquanji8","articleId":"d1dfef795c","start":492,"end":493}},"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6b1cf66e75","type":"paragraph","text":"致朱德等电”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"d1dfef795c"},{"id":"7768ac43eb","type":"paragraph","text":"接占包座捷电，无比欣感。红四方面军在包座略作休息，宜迅速北进：二方面军随后跟进到哈达铺后再大休息，免敌人封锁眠西线，北出发生困难","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"d1dfef795c"},{"id":"cf47fb045e","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年7月）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"d1dfef795c"},{"id":"d55563116d","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]红四方面军经过限苦酸涉，第三次通过了芜荣草地，到达班估、包座地区。是日，毛泽东和周恩来、彭德怀致电朱德、张国春、任时，告诉他们收到攻占包座的电报。这是电报的部分内容。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"d1dfef795c"}],"page":{"id":"165936a9bf","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"d1dfef795c","start":34,"end":34}}}},"__N_SSG":true}